            <p>
                <img src="../../../../Images/Shared/Al-Li/Alignment/Align-Segments6.png" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
            </p>
            <p>
                <img src="../../../../Images/Shared/Al-Li/Alignment/Align-Segments7.png" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
            </p>
            <MadCap:pageBreak MadCap:conditions="Lingo-Guides.Lingo-Alignment-Guide" />
            <p>When finished, you can upload the aligned segment(s) to your translation memory database.</p>
            <p>
                <img src="../../../../Images/Shared/Al-Li/Alignment/Align-Segments8.png" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
            </p>
